body: I was expecting the smaller girl to do those scat/feet smell from the others chapters, instead the author decided to give her a cock. My disappointment is immeasurable and my night is ruined.

Y’know, I don’t think a surprise entrance by a lamia, making it a 2 on 1, sounds like it’s in the rules. Speaking of, what’s the rules for fighting thing? If you can just appear with like 4 other people to murk this one guy, is it against the rules to just bring a fucking gun at that point?
Needs more focus on the snake girl.
